{"type": "article", "id": 26918, "title": "智能画框", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-17T06:45:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132419ca5Tf0oiD4FLxMHA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>要感谢不止提供视频和音乐的流媒体服务，你现在可以拥有一件会动的艺术品了：这个名为 Acanvas 的智能画框与一个艺术作品库相连，通过配套的手机应用你可以挑选自己喜欢的作品显示在“画布”上。Acanvas 另一个非常智能的设计在于它可以根据光线明暗在黑暗时自动降下连接线为自己充电，你可以根据需要将它和充电器放在家里的任何地方。你可以通过链接参与 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/acanvas/acanvas-the-cord-free-art-display-and-streaming-pl\">Acanvas</a> 的众筹，早鸟价为 299 美元（包含了艺术库的一年 120 美元的订阅费）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132414GLB02JitIqERzV7F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132415oqZJWzuM2VFHUwGT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132415paCc8JSwHkzK6Pm4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021324162thXOZH4Sz96kKVy.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}